---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import SectionBanner from '../../components/ui/SectionBanner.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Custom Rendering"
  description="Render farm access for 3ds Max, V-Ray Standalone, and Blender. We work with your scene, not just your files. Vision Graphics Kft., Budapest."
>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-rendering.jpg"
    label="When Your Files Won't Render"
    title="Custom Rendering"
    size="page"
    headingLevel="h1"
  />
  <div class="service-page">

    <div class="service-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/services/">Services</a>
      <span>→</span>
      <span>Custom Rendering</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Service</p>
    <h2 class="display-lg service-h1">Custom Rendering</h2>
    <p class="service-tagline-large">When your files won't render, we fix that.</p>

    <div class="service-body-grid">
      <div class="service-main">

        <p class="service-lead">
          Got a project that won't render? Don't have the hardware for an animation?
          We have a small render farm with 10–20 dedicated nodes. But here's what makes
          us different: we actually work with you, not just your files. 15+ years with V-Ray.
          We handle MAX files that crash everywhere else.
        </p>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">What we support</h2>
        <ul class="results-list">
          <li>3ds Max + V-Ray</li>
          <li>V-Ray Standalone</li>
          <li>Blender</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Render farm</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-list">
            <li>Own hardware, no shared queue</li>
            <li>10–20 dedicated nodes</li>
            <li>V-Ray Standalone</li>
            <li>Rush priority available</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Pricing</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-price">By scope</p>
          <p class="sidebar-note">Hourly for diagnostics. Render farm by node-hour. Quote within hours for urgent jobs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-cta">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary sidebar-btn">Send Your Scene</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-general.jpg"
    label="Who We Help"
    title="Built for Studios Like Yours"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      We built this service for architects, small visualization studios, and freelancers who
      create great work but hit hardware or time limits. Most render farms just process
      whatever you send them. We take the time to understand your project first.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Create great still renders but need help with animations</li>
      <li>Don't have the hardware for big or deadline-critical projects</li>
      <li>Want someone to talk to when things get stuck</li>
      <li>Have complex scenes that exhaust RAM on other machines</li>
      <li>Need to get a scene rendering without having to fix it yourself first</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-workflow.jpg"
    label="How We Work"
    title="More Than a Render Farm"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      First we discuss your goals and timeframe, then we look at your scene. Most render farms
      just process whatever you send them. We take time to prepare scenes properly — which
      means faster renders and lower costs for you.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Clean up heavy files before they hit the farm</li>
      <li>Fix geometry problems that cause render errors</li>
      <li>Sort out texture and asset issues</li>
      <li>Check render settings for efficiency</li>
      <li>Diagnose V-Ray artifacts, GI flickering, and exposure issues</li>
      <li>Set up render output pipelines with correct passes and elements</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-arch-viz.jpg"
    label="Why Work With Us"
    title="Real People, Real Results"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      We're not one of those huge, automated render farms. We've seen every rendering problem
      that production can produce — missing UVs, viewport vs. render discrepancies, light cache
      artifacts, proxy geometry failures — and we know the fastest path to fixing each one.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>You talk to real people who know 3D</li>
      <li>We help fix problems, not just render frames</li>
      <li>Consistent results delivered on time</li>
      <li>Own render farm — no competing for nodes on urgent jobs</li>
      <li>Legacy scene conversion: update older MAX scenes to current V-Ray standards</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

</Page>

<style>
  .service-page {
    max-width: 1060px;
    padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .service-breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 200ms; }
  .service-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .service-h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-tagline-large { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h6); font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-lead { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .service-body-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .service-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .service-section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  /* Sub-sections */
  .service-section { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }

  .section-body { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .results-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .results-list li { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .results-list li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-accent); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }

  /* Sidebar */
  .service-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 5rem; }
  .sidebar-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .sidebar-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .sidebar-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.35rem; }
  .sidebar-list li { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 0.9rem; position: relative; }
  .sidebar-list li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-border); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }
  .sidebar-price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h5); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-note { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-body-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .service-sidebar { position: static; }
  }
</style>
